  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >miKaPyon is a rabbit in a colorful 3D platformer full of fast freerunning and jump challenges, wall-jumps and sliding over hills and loops. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reach for the Stars ☆ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your tasks: reach goals, collect stars, moons and beat best-times! <br>You can not \"die\" but fall, slide, bounce around and drop your stars. <br>The world is friendly but challenging! Explore at your own pace. <br>Use stars to reach new places! The sky is the limit ... or is it?</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >miKaPyon is a rabbit in a colorful 3D platformer full of fast freerunning and jump challenges, wall-jumps and sliding over hills and loops. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reach for the Stars ☆ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your tasks: reach goals, collect stars, moons and beat best-times! <br>You can not \"die\" but fall, slide, bounce around and drop your stars. <br>The world is friendly but challenging! Explore at your own pace. <br>Use stars to reach new places! The sky is the limit ... or is it?</p>",
